{"type": "article", "id": 46271, "title": "Dior 回应形象大使争议，以及，上海时装周落幕 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-10-19T03:54:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3559, "name": "上海时装周"}, {"id": 17255, "name": "KITH"}, {"id": 4125, "name": "京东"}, {"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}, {"id": 44164, "name": "Puma"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171019112343sgRE6SrLGtzFoH1f.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/business-features/dior-defends-china-influencer-strategy-reopens-shanghai-flagship-11029885/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Dior 重开中国旗舰店，回应形象大使争议 </strong></a>| 昨日，Dior 位于上海恒隆广场的中国区旗舰店全新开幕，这是中国首个集齐女装、男装系列以及精品首饰和手表的旗舰店。开幕活动后，Dior 的首席执行官 Sidney Toledano 在接受采访时对品牌形象大使人选的争议作出回应，表示不认同部分观点，并透露新的形象大使成功吸引了年轻一代的消费者。今年，Dior 先后任命 Angelababy 和赵丽颖成为品牌形象大使。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/puma-raises-full-year-target-q3-sales-rise-11029957/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>第三季度销售额大涨 17%，Puma 提高全年盈利展望</strong></a> | 在截止至 9 月 30 日的三个月内，Puma 的销售额同比上涨 17%，至 11.2 亿欧元。营业利润预计猛涨 68.3% 至 1.01 亿欧元。Puma 因此上调全年业绩预期，预计销售额降增长 14% 至 16%，利润有望达到 2.35 亿至 2.45 亿欧元。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/zalando-earnings-third-quarter-beauty-launch-11029865/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>德国电商巨头 Zalando 将在明年开启美妆事业</strong></a> | 日前，Zalando 宣布将于明年进军美妆市场，其业务范围将涉及护肤、香水和化妆品等产品。Zalando 打算在柏林开设一家美妆概念店，定期举办活动，并推出美妆教程。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>纽约街头潮店 <a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/10/17/kith-fall-2017-collection/\" rel=\"nofollow\">KITH 正式发布 2017 秋冬 lookbook</a>，演绎了多种质朴的毛衣穿法...另外，KITH 还与 Timberland 再度合作，推出两款全新配色的 Field Boot。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019111244WlsegwbcDG0fEqXS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019111245RV2Lfj5ulPD8I94U.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019111245dXijULzIo8OYAGWM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019111247vIwGFad17DjqO0rW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019111247wG7ibAQqxmRdr0pc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019111249Yt3ks0JEITSgX8h6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017101911124930xoEH1nyZTS6pJW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019111249FURTZhx9vcEidXSL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019111249zjLJAmiSMBhgIRVr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019111250tPOp8Dkb043nKLFs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019111252fONZLi73Ul2d8CEv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017101911125279bFThponCZl5PwK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019111252v5XAoD48Yz1mcwMC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019111252QI71YlMTcJkh3geu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019111254ylwprv7TJ54EieYa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019111254QGE5SrFI30YTzMw7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019111255BXlAH1YmLdfKs2Tk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019111255t3lu5DbCwqhnykF4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>宫下贵裕主理的 <a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/10/18/takahiromiyashita-soloist-ss18/\" rel=\"nofollow\">TAKAHIROMIYASHITAThe SoloIst </a>在东京发布了 2018 春夏系列。一如即往地，很硬核、很朋克，还有点吓人。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019110935EathYsqnLrQlm1w8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019110935Bbx70PZmJIRGiu2g.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019110935hk0zlmufEwr4SUMt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019110937CbVWSFfuhJcdmAKT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710191109374Wkf31MUu9PnytBF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019110937tLCFbrP1Qgv0A7zI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019110937WEaoG5pv2KRbO6sD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019110939e3DTAnNtLIFEVJ0k.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019110940S0CmRciqDJzWbj8p.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017101911094007BgxEAPd8ebcU29.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019110941RhNqUG9ZxgtYb0TD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019110941hnIt1eTaZPyfFMuE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019110942NE1stlO2VSRkLH45.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019110942e39hqj5Xoa4VPCp6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710191109422UthKucM0ap7yWxv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>盆栽哥 <a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/10/the-weeknd-puma-xo-collection-second-drop\" rel=\"nofollow\">The Weeknd </a>以个人品牌 XO 的名义，与 Puma 的第二波联名也来了。该系列以 Deluxe Denim 为主题，包括和服风格大衣、牛仔裤、夹克、冷帽等多款单品，将于 10 月 26 日正式发售。 </p><p>先来看看 lookbook：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019110853kaKYM9eld2rDVjEy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666456\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017101911085035fl0TtiNdsUeJMW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666456\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019110856UBm9ifs182IkFJCN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666456\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710191108562IoSXQjmK1BG9sFg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666456\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019110857QPbm5GwBr9SzReCW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666456\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019110858qf24A60KBi5eYMNI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666456\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019110858nKY5Lk2Nm1ujz0tD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666456\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>上海时装周的新品发布于昨日正式结束。</p><p>最后一天里，依然没什么值得一看的。</p><p>京东与品牌 ALL COMES FROM NOTHING 合作的秀，发布了“东方罂粟”的主题系列；张帅的个人同名品牌 ZHANG SHUAI 与京东共同举办了上海时装周首秀。</p><p>上海本土品牌 JI CHENG 带来了“鸟人”系列；Vmajor 的主题是“环球旅行的世界公民”，运用了大地色系和棉麻材质试图表达复古文化。</p><p><strong>ALL COMES FROM NOTHING：</strong><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019111634HRwX1Ap67G2zi0Zj.png\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019111637dHRb64CWDEkOvyeh.png\" data-ratio=\"1.680352\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019111638etnA7CBKFEr65cIf.png\" data-ratio=\"1.511936\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019111639Rar9LzAFxoUEgOGS.png\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019111639KgxDvbuzmW9cdSpA.png\" data-ratio=\"1.497368\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710191116409xuPleLf6SawzRKh.png\" data-ratio=\"1.521277\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019111642FGK2usUwC3WEQPpn.png\" data-ratio=\"1.505291\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710191116426K8XwFaMN0VgRCni.png\" data-ratio=\"1.498681\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201710191116431ezja6cghGwNp79J.png\" data-ratio=\"1.498688\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p><strong>ZHANGSHUAI：</strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20171019112144fixvT3b58YAGpgqQ.jpg\" d